These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, juice
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, photography
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, entrepreneur
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, thriller
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, bird
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, roller
1. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is the chinese##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | juice     | tea       |
| Hobby         | gardening   | photography     |
| Job           | teacher | entrepreneur   |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller   | mystery  |
| Nationality   | chinese | brazilian |
| Pet           | chinchilla      | bird     |
| Transport     | roller    | car   |

