.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, juice
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, skydiving
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, mechanic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, funk
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, mexican
2 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, subway
1. the mechanic is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is the person driving the subway##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the fan of classical##1
4. the mexican is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking water is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | water    | juice |
| Hobby         | skydiving        | photography  |
| Job           | bartender | mechanic  |
| Music-Genre   | funk            | classical    |
| Nationality   | malaysian     | mexican   |
| Pet           | dog         | hedgehog    |
| Transport     | helicopter           | subway      |

